<div style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: "Helvetica Neue"; min-height: 15px;'><br></div>
<div style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: "Helvetica Neue";'>2. Ako trebamo zadržati osobne podatke za svoje pravne, porezne, revizijske i računovodstvene obveze, zadržat ćemo potrebne osobne podatke tijekom razdoblja koje zahtijeva primjenjivi zakon; i/ili,</div>
<div style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: "Helvetica Neue"; min-height: 15px;'><br></div>
